CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 13, 1957, page B6, reads: "Supervisors at Loblaws - Left to right: Carl Downer, assistant manager; Clarence Koerntgen, grocery manager, and William Tobin, meat manager."
TitMainTitle: Loblaw's Grocery Store employees, left to right: assistant manager, Carl Downer; grocery manager, Clarence Koerntgen; and meat manager, William Tobin,, standing in aisle at Loblaw's Market, with map of Ohio, Pennsylvania and New York on wall in background
